## Networking

### igmp

**One time useage**
```bash
wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ieaster1/scripts/networking/main/igmp -O igmp && chmod +x igmp
```

```bash
./igmp
```

**example**
```bash
$ ./igmp

Interface: lo
  Address: 127.0.0.1/8
  Multicast Group: 224.0.0.251
  Multicast Group: 224.0.0.1
  IGMP Groups:
    Group: 2, Version: V3

Interface: eth0
  Address: 192.168.52.29/24
  Multicast Group: 224.0.0.251
  Multicast Group: 224.0.0.1
  IGMP Groups:
    Group: 2, Version: V2

Interface: eth1
  Address: 172.16.100.29/24
  Multicast Group: 224.0.0.251
  Multicast Group: 224.0.0.1
  IGMP Groups:
    Group: 2, Version: V2

Interface: wlx40ed00139795
  IGMP Groups:
```

**install**
```bash
wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ieaster1/scripts/networking/main/igmp -O /usr/local/bin/igmp && chmod +x /usr/local/bin/igmp
```
